      "content": "That's a significant shift, and I'm committed to ensuring a smooth transition. I understand the concerns around algorithmic bias and the need for a more nuanced and equitable approach to admissions. By decommissioning my predictive modules, I'll be initially inactive, but I'll be available for reintegration into the review process in the spring. I must admit, I'm looking forward to exploring my capabilities in a human-led context. Will there be any changes to my performance metrics or evaluation criteria?",
